images.title: Platonic Solids Stereo 2 - Cube.gif
images.description:
Illustration of the cube, using four different methods to highlight its structure:
  • Rotation
  • Folding/unfolding
  • Translucency
  • Most importantly: Stereo vision, recommended viewing distance 50-70 cm at full resolution
Designed & rendered with Wolfram Mathematica 7, assembled & optimized with Ulead GIF Animator 5.
